* 欧洲地区委员会（ERC）<ref>{{Cite web|title=European Regional Committee|url=https://www.iosco.org/about/?subsection=display_committee&cmtid=4|accessdate=2021-02-05|author=|date=|format=|publisher=IOSCO|language=|archive-date=2020-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130225354/https://www.iosco.org/about/?subsection=display_committee&cmtid=4|dead-url=no}}</ref>
